description.content:
Located opposite Jaipur's Nehru Sahkar Bhawan, 5 BY OYO Metropolitan features a rooftop swimming pool and spa. It also offers its guests free parking privileges and a fitness center.

Rooms at this hotel are fitted with a flat-screen TV providing cable channels. A minibar and tea and coffee-making facilities are provided. Each room has a safety deposit box.

Guests can enjoy getting a tan at the sun deck or relax at the sauna. A tour desk is available for guests to make sightseeing arrangements. Car rental and 24-hour currency exchange services are also available.

5 Alley offers 24-hour dining of authentic Rajasthani dishes and continental cuisine. Drinks and snacks are served at Salud.

5 BY OYO Metropolitan is 800 meters from Jaipur City Center. Jaipur Railway Station and Dolls Museum are 3 km from the hotel.
